In this solidity contract, we will help you make a fundraising contract from scratch. Few of the real use cases of this contract can be in the applications where there is a need for transparency in fund transfer.
Following are the organizations that can make an application based on this contract:

1. Non-Profit organizations (NPOs)
2. Non-Government Organizations (NGOs)
3. Fundraising platforms for startups, etc.

# Description

Below mentioned are the points that have been considered while writing this contract but are not limited to these. A user may also add his/her logic while making this smart contract.
There is no limit to raising the funds.
1. Anyone can add any amount.
2. The ownerâ€™s address is hardcoded that allows only him/her to withdraw funds at any point in time.
3. Anyone can view the current balance in the contract.
